        "action": "Raise the minimum wage for those working between 9pm and 7am to \u00a314 p/h",
        "additional_details": "Tesco\u2014who made a \u00a31\u00b76bl profit last quarter\u2014pay staff near minimum wage to work until midnight. Clubs hire 18\u201321-year-olds at \u00a35.60/h till 5.The real living wage in the U.K. is nearly \u00a310/h: https://bbc.in/2JGrY0b This work is unhealthy and those employed deserve compensation.\r\n\r\nStudy noting an increase in the risk of an early death amongst night-shift workers: https://www.theguardian.com/sustainable-business/2015/oct/28/night-shift-three-million-workers-health-risks-obesity-cancer-diabetes\r\n\r\nRadio 4 on damage to organs and the brain caused by nightwork: https://www.ajpmonline.org/article/S0749-3797(14)00623-0/fulltext\r\n\r\nhttps://www.psych.ox.ac.uk/news/how-can-working-night-shifts-affect-mental-and-physical-health",
        "background": "Workers of late shifts\u2014which have been proven to have detrimental effects on health\u2014are increasingly common, and these workers are being exploited.",
